preference.name: CRF_PLMXML_export_supported_types
preference.preference_description: Contains the list of types which are supported for PLMXML Reports. The purpose of this preference is to work with PLMXML_export_supported_types to define supported types for Item Reports with PLMXML format. If some unsupported type is added, the behavior is undefined.
